'''客船'''是主要用于运送[[乘客|乘客]]的大型船隻。分為[[渡轮|渡轮]]（Ferries）、[[遠洋客轮|遠洋客轮]]（Ocean Liners）和[[游輪|游輪]]（Cruise Ships）。渡船的航線通常是帶旅客穿越水體或是只有一日或一夜的短程運輸<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefreedictionary.com/ferry|title=ferry|work=TheFreeDictionary.com|accessdate=2012-07-07|archive-date=2012-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120522125549/http://www.thefreedictionary.com/ferry|dead-url=no}}</ref>；遠洋客船則是長途的航行；遊船通常沒有運輸功能，其主要的目的是娛樂，航程結束後通常會將遊客載往原出發點下船。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessdictionary.com/definition/cruise-ship.html|title=What is cruise ship? definition and meaning|work=BusinessDictionary.com|accessdate=2012-07-07|archive-date=2012-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120713072818/http://www.businessdictionary.com/definition/cruise-ship.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

